1,690 reviews
#2 Best Value of 778 places to stay in Thua Thien - Hue Province
Centrally located hotel in Hue with early check-in and friendly staff. Convenient access to attractions, cafes, and river. Clean, comfortable rooms and relaxing pool area. On-site Spice Viet restaurant offering authentic cuisine. Ideal for business and leisure travelers.
