#5 Best Value of 778 places to stay in Thua Thien - Hue Province
Nature-inspired resort with a variety of activities, large pool, and nearby golf course. Luxurious, spacious rooms offer sea views and environmentally-friendly design. Dining options and serene atmosphere.
6. TTC Imperial Hotel
1,778 reviews
#6 Best Value of 778 places to stay in Thua Thien - Hue Province
Elegant 5-star hotel near Perfume River, boasting stunning river views and harmonious East-West architecture. Spacious, well-appointed junior suites and corner rooms with modern amenities. Rooftop bar offers 360-degree city views and a temple on the 17th floor. Convenient location with friendly staff.
